<phyphox xmlns="https://phyphox.org/xml" xmlns:editor="https://phyphox.org/xml/editor" version="1.19">
  <title>基于光敏计时器的瞬时速度</title>
  <category>工具</category>
  <icon format="base64"></icon>
  <description>本工具基于phyphox官方的“Camera stopwatch: Brightness”实验改造而来。
测量亮度发生变化的时间间隔，例如由物体经过引起的变化。并借助用户输入的物体间距近似地计算出这一过程中的瞬时速度。请注意：实际运动速度越快，测量误差越小。
此配置允许你为测量矩形区域内的平均亮度（更具体地说是光亮度）设置一个下限阈值和一个上限阈值。如果亮度超过上限阈值或低于下限阈值，当前时间将被记录为一个触发事件。系统会记录不同事件之间的时间间隔以及这些事件的持续时间。
时间分辨率由摄像头的预览帧率决定，通常固定为 30fps，因此采样率为 33 毫秒。请注意，Phyphox 使用的是摄像头的预览流进行实时分析，其速率受限于此。如果你的手机支持高速或慢动作录制，更高的帧率仅适用于录制模式（而非实时模式），而 Phyphox 目前并未使用录制模式。
如果你使用自动曝光，请注意平均亮度会在短时间内漂移到 0.5 左右。这可能允许在光线变化的条件下进行可靠的触发，但也可能会影响触发和特别是测量持续时间的精度。另外请注意，此秒表使用的是亮度（luma）而非光亮度（luminance），即一种可以更快计算出的亮度的非线性表示。这意味着该值将无法与光亮度测量值进行比较，并且会受到曝光设置变化的影响。
如果你愿意减小自动曝光带来的误差，你可以点击摄像头预览框并将下方的“AE”设置为“off”</description>
  <data-containers>
    <container size="0">inLuma</container>
    <container size="0">thisLuma</container>
    <container>luma_last</container>
    <container>t_last</container>
    <container>t_limit</container>
    <container size="0">inT</container>
    <container size="0">triggering</container>
    <container size="0">triggering_change</container>
    <container init="0.3">threshold_low</container>
    <container init="0.7">threshold_high</container>
    <container init="1">outside</container>
    <container size="0">amplitude</container>
    <container size="0">t</container>
    <container size="0">onEvents</container>
    <container size="0">offEvents</container>
    <container size="0">dtlist</container>
    <container size="0">ddlist</container>
    <container size="0">tindex</container>
    <container>tcount</container>
    <container>tcount-1</container>
    <container>avgInterval</container>
    <container>avgRate</container>
    <container>avgBPM</container>
    <container init="0">on0</container>
    <container init="0">on1</container>
    <container init="0">on2</container>
    <container init="0">on3</container>
    <container init="0">on4</container>
    <container init="0">on5</container>
    <container init="0">off0</container>
    <container init="0">off1</container>
    <container init="0">off2</container>
    <container init="0">off3</container>
    <container init="0">off4</container>
    <container init="0">off5</container>
    <container>don0</container>
    <container>don1</container>
    <container>don2</container>
    <container>don3</container>
    <container>don4</container>
    <container>don5</container>
    <container>dt01</container>
    <container>dt02</container>
    <container>dt03</container>
    <container>dt04</container>
    <container>dt05</container>
    <container>dt12</container>
    <container>dt23</container>
    <container>dt34</container>
    <container>dt45</container>
    <container init="0">reset</container>
    <container size="5">lastTimes</container>
    <container size="0">lastPeriods</container>
    <container>framePeriod</container>
    <container>frameRate</container>
    <container size="0">X</container>
    <container size="0">V</container>
    <container size="0">thelastdt</container>
  </data-containers>
  <input>
    <camera x1="0.4" x2="0.6" y1="0.4" y2="0.6" aeStrategy="prioritizeFramerate">
      <output component="luma">inLuma</output>
      <output component="t">inT</output>
    </camera>
  </input>
  <analysis>
    <append>
      <input keep="true">inLuma</input>
      <output append="true">amplitude</output>
    </append>
    <append>
      <input keep="true">inT</input>
      <output append="true">t</output>
    </append>
    <append>
      <input keep="true">inLuma</input>
      <input>luma_last</input>
      <output>luma_last</output>
    </append>
    <append>
      <input>luma_last</input>
      <input>inLuma</input>
      <output>thisLuma</output>
    </append>
    <append>
      <input keep="true">thisLuma</input>
      <output>luma_last</output>
    </append>
    <append>
      <input keep="true">t</input>
      <output>t_last</output>
    </append>
    <subtract>
      <input>t_last</input>
      <input type="value">10</input>
      <output>t_limit</output>
    </subtract>
    <rangefilter>
      <input as="in">t</input>
      <input as="min">t_limit</input>
      <input as="in">amplitude</input>
      <output as="out">t</output>
      <output as="out">amplitude</output>
    </rangefilter>
    <formula formula="min((1-heaviside([4]))*(heaviside([1_]-[3]) * heaviside([2]-[1_])) + (heaviside([4]))*(heaviside([1_]-[2]) + heaviside([3]-[1_])),1)">
      <input>thisLuma</input>
      <input keep="true">threshold_high</input>
      <input keep="true">threshold_low</input>
      <input keep="true">outside</input>
      <output>triggering</output>
    </formula>
    <differentiate>
      <input as="in" keep="true">triggering</input>
      <output>triggering_change</output>
    </differentiate>
    <rangefilter>
      <input as="in" keep="true">inT</input>
      <input as="in" keep="true">triggering_change</input>
      <input as="min" type="value">0.5</input>
      <output as="out" append="true">onEvents</output>
    </rangefilter>
    <rangefilter>
      <input as="in">inT</input>
      <input as="in">triggering_change</input>
      <input as="max" type="value">-0.5</input>
      <output as="out" append="true">offEvents</output>
    </rangefilter>
    <append>
      <input keep="true">t</input>
      <output>on0</output>
    </append>
    <append>
      <input keep="true">t</input>
      <output>on1</output>
    </append>
    <append>
      <input keep="true">t</input>
      <output>on2</output>
    </append>
    <append>
      <input keep="true">t</input>
      <output>on3</output>
    </append>
    <append>
      <input keep="true">t</input>
      <output>on4</output>
    </append>
    <append>
      <input keep="true">t</input>
      <output>on5</output>
    </append>
    <append>
      <input keep="true">t</input>
      <output>off0</output>
    </append>
    <append>
      <input keep="true">t</input>
      <output>off1</output>
    </append>
    <append>
      <input keep="true">t</input>
      <output>off2</output>
    </append>
    <append>
      <input keep="true">t</input>
      <output>off3</output>
    </append>
    <append>
      <input keep="true">t</input>
      <output>off4</output>
    </append>
    <append>
      <input keep="true">t</input>
      <output>off5</output>
    </append>
    <if greater="true">
      <input as="a" keep="true">reset</input>
      <input type="value" as="b">0</input>
      <input type="empty" as="true"/>
      <output>amplitude</output>
    </if>
    <if greater="true">
      <input as="a" keep="true">reset</input>
      <input type="value" as="b">0</input>
      <input type="empty" as="true"/>
      <output>t</output>
    </if>
    <if greater="true">
      <input as="a" keep="true">reset</input>
      <input type="value" as="b">0</input>
      <input type="empty" as="true"/>
      <output>luma_last</output>
    </if>
    <if greater="true">
      <input as="a" keep="true">reset</input>
      <input type="value" as="b">0</input>
      <input type="empty" as="true"/>
      <output>onEvents</output>
    </if>
    <if greater="true">
      <input as="a" keep="true">reset</input>
      <input type="value" as="b">0</input>
      <input type="empty" as="true"/>
      <output>offEvents</output>
    </if>
    <if greater="true">
      <input as="a" keep="true">reset</input>
      <input type="value" as="b">0</input>
      <input type="empty" as="true"/>
      <output>inT</output>
    </if>
    <if greater="true">
      <input as="a" keep="true">reset</input>
      <input type="value" as="b">0</input>
      <input type="empty" as="true"/>
      <output>inLuma</output>
    </if>
    <append>
      <input type="value">0</input>
      <output>reset</output>
    </append>
    <subrange>
      <input as="in" keep="true">onEvents</input>
      <input as="from" type="value">0</input>
      <input as="length" type="value">1</input>
      <output as="out" append="true">on0</output>
    </subrange>
    <subrange>
      <input as="in" keep="true">onEvents</input>
      <input as="from" type="value">1</input>
      <input as="length" type="value">1</input>
      <output as="out" append="true">on1</output>
    </subrange>
    <subrange>
      <input as="in" keep="true">onEvents</input>
      <input as="from" type="value">2</input>
      <input as="length" type="value">1</input>
      <output as="out" append="true">on2</output>
    </subrange>
    <subrange>
      <input as="in" keep="true">onEvents</input>
      <input as="from" type="value">3</input>
      <input as="length" type="value">1</input>
      <output as="out" append="true">on3</output>
    </subrange>
    <subrange>
      <input as="in" keep="true">onEvents</input>
      <input as="from" type="value">4</input>
      <input as="length" type="value">1</input>
      <output as="out" append="true">on4</output>
    </subrange>
    <subrange>
      <input as="in" keep="true">onEvents</input>
      <input as="from" type="value">5</input>
      <input as="length" type="value">1</input>
      <output as="out" append="true">on5</output>
    </subrange>
    <subrange>
      <input as="in" keep="true">offEvents</input>
      <input as="from" type="value">0</input>
      <input as="length" type="value">1</input>
      <output as="out" append="true">off0</output>
    </subrange>
    <subrange>
      <input as="in" keep="true">offEvents</input>
      <input as="from" type="value">1</input>
      <input as="length" type="value">1</input>
      <output as="out" append="true">off1</output>
    </subrange>
    <subrange>
      <input as="in" keep="true">offEvents</input>
      <input as="from" type="value">2</input>
      <input as="length" type="value">1</input>
      <output as="out" append="true">off2</output>
    </subrange>
    <subrange>
      <input as="in" keep="true">offEvents</input>
      <input as="from" type="value">3</input>
      <input as="length" type="value">1</input>
      <output as="out" append="true">off3</output>
    </subrange>
    <subrange>
      <input as="in" keep="true">offEvents</input>
      <input as="from" type="value">4</input>
      <input as="length" type="value">1</input>
      <output as="out" append="true">off4</output>
    </subrange>
    <subrange>
      <input as="in" keep="true">offEvents</input>
      <input as="from" type="value">5</input>
      <input as="length" type="value">1</input>
      <output as="out" append="true">off5</output>
    </subrange>
    <subtract>
      <input keep="true">on1</input>
      <input keep="true">on0</input>
      <output>dt01</output>
    </subtract>
    <subtract>
      <input keep="true">on2</input>
      <input keep="true">on0</input>
      <output>dt02</output>
    </subtract>
    <subtract>
      <input keep="true">on3</input>
      <input keep="true">on0</input>
      <output>dt03</output>
    </subtract>
    <subtract>
      <input keep="true">on4</input>
      <input keep="true">on0</input>
      <output>dt04</output>
    </subtract>
    <subtract>
      <input keep="true">on5</input>
      <input keep="true">on0</input>
      <output>dt05</output>
    </subtract>
    <subtract>
      <input keep="true">on2</input>
      <input keep="true">on1</input>
      <output>dt12</output>
    </subtract>
    <subtract>
      <input keep="true">on3</input>
      <input keep="true">on2</input>
      <output>dt23</output>
    </subtract>
    <subtract>
      <input keep="true">on4</input>
      <input keep="true">on3</input>
      <output>dt34</output>
    </subtract>
    <subtract>
      <input keep="true">on5</input>
      <input keep="true">on4</input>
      <output>dt45</output>
    </subtract>
    <subtract>
      <input keep="true">off0</input>
      <input keep="true">on0</input>
      <output>don0</output>
    </subtract>
    <subtract>
      <input keep="true">off1</input>
      <input keep="true">on1</input>
      <output>don1</output>
    </subtract>
    <subtract>
      <input keep="true">off2</input>
      <input keep="true">on2</input>
      <output>don2</output>
    </subtract>
    <subtract>
      <input keep="true">off3</input>
      <input keep="true">on3</input>
      <output>don3</output>
    </subtract>
    <subtract>
      <input keep="true">off4</input>
      <input keep="true">on4</input>
      <output>don4</output>
    </subtract>
    <subtract>
      <input keep="true">off5</input>
      <input keep="true">on5</input>
      <output>don5</output>
    </subtract>
    <if less="true" equal="true">
      <input as="a" keep="true">dt01</input>
      <input type="value" as="b">0</input>
      <input type="empty" as="true"/>
      <output>dt01</output>
    </if>
    <if less="true" equal="true">
      <input as="a" keep="true">dt02</input>
      <input type="value" as="b">0</input>
      <input type="empty" as="true"/>
      <output>dt02</output>
    </if>
    <if less="true" equal="true">
      <input as="a" keep="true">dt03</input>
      <input type="value" as="b">0</input>
      <input type="empty" as="true"/>
      <output>dt03</output>
    </if>
    <if less="true" equal="true">
      <input as="a" keep="true">dt04</input>
      <input type="value" as="b">0</input>
      <input type="empty" as="true"/>
      <output>dt04</output>
    </if>
    <if less="true" equal="true">
      <input as="a" keep="true">dt05</input>
      <input type="value" as="b">0</input>
      <input type="empty" as="true"/>
      <output>dt05</output>
    </if>
    <if less="true" equal="true">
      <input as="a" keep="true">dt12</input>
      <input type="value" as="b">0</input>
      <input type="empty" as="true"/>
      <output>dt12</output>
    </if>
    <if less="true" equal="true">
      <input as="a" keep="true">dt23</input>
      <input type="value" as="b">0</input>
      <input type="empty" as="true"/>
      <output>dt23</output>
    </if>
    <if less="true" equal="true">
      <input as="a" keep="true">dt34</input>
      <input type="value" as="b">0</input>
      <input type="empty" as="true"/>
      <output>dt34</output>
    </if>
    <if less="true" equal="true">
      <input as="a" keep="true">dt45</input>
      <input type="value" as="b">0</input>
      <input type="empty" as="true"/>
      <output>dt45</output>
    </if>
    <if less="true" equal="true">
      <input as="a" keep="true">don0</input>
      <input type="value" as="b">0</input>
      <input type="empty" as="true"/>
      <output>don0</output>
    </if>
    <if less="true" equal="true">
      <input as="a" keep="true">don1</input>
      <input type="value" as="b">0</input>
      <input type="empty" as="true"/>
      <output>don1</output>
    </if>
    <if less="true" equal="true">
      <input as="a" keep="true">don2</input>
      <input type="value" as="b">0</input>
      <input type="empty" as="true"/>
      <output>don2</output>
    </if>
    <if less="true" equal="true">
      <input as="a" keep="true">don3</input>
      <input type="value" as="b">0</input>
      <input type="empty" as="true"/>
      <output>don3</output>
    </if>
    <if less="true" equal="true">
      <input as="a" keep="true">don4</input>
      <input type="value" as="b">0</input>
      <input type="empty" as="true"/>
      <output>don4</output>
    </if>
    <if less="true" equal="true">
      <input as="a" keep="true">don5</input>
      <input type="value" as="b">0</input>
      <input type="empty" as="true"/>
      <output>don5</output>
    </if>
    <append>
      <input keep="true">t</input>
      <output>lastTimes</output>
    </append>
    <differentiate>
      <input as="in" keep="true">lastTimes</input>
      <output>lastPeriods</output>
    </differentiate>
    <average>
      <input as="buffer">lastPeriods</input>
      <output>framePeriod</output>
    </average>
    <divide>
      <input type="value">1</input>
      <input keep="true">framePeriod</input>
      <output>frameRate</output>
    </divide>
    <differentiate>
      <input as="in" keep="true">onEvents</input>
      <output>dtlist</output>
    </differentiate>
    <average>
      <input as="buffer" keep="true">dtlist</input>
      <output>avgInterval</output>
    </average>
    <divide>
      <input keep="true">X</input>
      <input keep="true">dtlist</input>
      <output>V</output>
    </divide>
    <append>
      <input keep="true">dtlist</input>
      <output>thelastdt</output>
    </append>
    <divide>
      <input type="value">1</input>
      <input keep="true">avgInterval</input>
      <output>avgRate</output>
    </divide>
    <multiply>
      <input keep="true">avgRate</input>
      <input type="value">60</input>
      <output>avgBPM</output>
    </multiply>
    <append>
      <input type="value">0</input>
      <input>dtlist</input>
      <input type="value">0</input>
      <output>dtlist</output>
    </append>
    <subtract>
      <input keep="true">offEvents</input>
      <input keep="true">onEvents</input>
      <output>ddlist</output>
    </subtract>
    <append>
      <input type="value">0</input>
      <output append="true">ddlist</output>
    </append>
    <count>
      <input as="buffer" keep="true">ddlist</input>
      <output>tcount</output>
    </count>
    <subtract>
      <input keep="true">tcount</input>
      <input type="value">1</input>
      <output>tcount-1</output>
    </subtract>
    <ramp>
      <input as="start" type="value">0</input>
      <input as="stop">tcount-1</input>
      <input as="length">tcount</input>
      <output>tindex</output>
    </ramp>
  </analysis>
  <views>
    <view label="设置">
      <camera-gui label="Preview" exposure_adjustment_level="3" showControls="always"/>
      <slider label="Trigger range" type="range" minValue="0" maxValue="1" stepSize="0.01">
        <output value="lowerValue">threshold_low</output>
        <output value="upperValue">threshold_high</output>
      </slider>
      <dropdown label="Trigger">
        <output>outside</output>
        <map value="1">outside range</map>
        <map value="-1">inside range</map>
      </dropdown>
      <value label="State">
        <input>triggering</input>
        <map max="0.5">Idle</map>
        <map min="0.5">Triggered</map>
      </value>
      <separator height="1"/>
      <graph label="Luma" partialUpdate="true" labelX="[[quantity_short_time]]" labelY="[[quantity_short_luma]]" unitX="[[unit_short_second]]">
        <input axis="x">t</input>
        <input axis="y">amplitude</input>
      </graph>
      <separator height="1"/>
      <value label="Frame rate" precision="1" unit="[[unit_short_hertz]]">
        <input>frameRate</input>
      </value>
    </view>
    <view label="速度">
      <edit label="灯光间距" signed="false" unit="m" default="12">
        <output>X</output>
      </edit>
      <info label="注：地铁灯光间距约为12m" color="weakwhite" italic="true" align="center"/>
      <value label="时间变化量" unit="秒">
        <input>thelastdt</input>
      </value>
      <value label="已进行时间" unit="秒">
        <input>onEvents</input>
      </value>
      <value label="速度" color="green" size="3" unit="m/s">
        <input>V</input>
      </value>
      <value label="速度" color="green" size="3" unit="km/h" factor="3.6">
        <input>V</input>
      </value>
      <graph label="速度——时间" labelX="时刻" labelY="（近似）瞬时速度" unitX="秒" unitY="m/s">
        <input axis="x">onEvents</input>
        <input axis="y">V</input>
      </graph>
    </view>
    <view label="序列">
      <value label="时间 1" size="3" precision="2" unit="[[unit_short_second]]">
        <input>dt01</input>
      </value>
      <value label="时间 2" size="3" precision="2" unit="[[unit_short_second]]">
        <input>dt12</input>
      </value>
      <value label="时间 3" size="3" precision="2" unit="[[unit_short_second]]">
        <input>dt23</input>
      </value>
      <value label="时间 4" size="3" precision="2" unit="[[unit_short_second]]">
        <input>dt34</input>
      </value>
      <value label="时间 5" size="3" precision="2" unit="[[unit_short_second]]">
        <input>dt45</input>
      </value>
      <separator height="1"/>
      <button label="复位">
        <input type="value">1</input>
        <output>reset</output>
      </button>
    </view>
    <view label="并行">
      <value label="时间 1" size="3" precision="2" unit="[[unit_short_second]]">
        <input>dt01</input>
      </value>
      <value label="时间 2" size="3" precision="2" unit="[[unit_short_second]]">
        <input>dt02</input>
      </value>
      <value label="时间 3" size="3" precision="2" unit="[[unit_short_second]]">
        <input>dt03</input>
      </value>
      <value label="时间 4" size="3" precision="2" unit="[[unit_short_second]]">
        <input>dt04</input>
      </value>
      <value label="时间 5" size="3" precision="2" unit="[[unit_short_second]]">
        <input>dt05</input>
      </value>
      <separator height="1"/>
      <button label="复位">
        <input type="value">1</input>
        <output>reset</output>
      </button>
    </view>
    <view label="持续时长">
      <value label="触发持续 0" size="3" precision="2" unit="[[unit_short_second]]">
        <input>don0</input>
      </value>
      <value label="触发持续 1" size="3" precision="2" unit="[[unit_short_second]]">
        <input>don1</input>
      </value>
      <value label="触发持续 2" size="3" precision="2" unit="[[unit_short_second]]">
        <input>don2</input>
      </value>
      <value label="触发持续 3" size="3" precision="2" unit="[[unit_short_second]]">
        <input>don3</input>
      </value>
      <value label="触发持续 4" size="3" precision="2" unit="[[unit_short_second]]">
        <input>don4</input>
      </value>
      <value label="触发持续 5" size="3" precision="2" unit="[[unit_short_second]]">
        <input>don5</input>
      </value>
      <separator height="1"/>
      <button label="复位">
        <input type="value">1</input>
        <output>reset</output>
      </button>
    </view>
    <view label="触发器">
      <value label="触发起始 0" size="1" precision="2" unit="[[unit_short_second]]">
        <input>on0</input>
      </value>
      <value label="触发结束 0" size="1" precision="2" unit="[[unit_short_second]]">
        <input>off0</input>
      </value>
      <separator height="1"/>
      <value label="触发起始 1" size="1" precision="2" unit="[[unit_short_second]]">
        <input>on1</input>
      </value>
      <value label="触发结束 1" size="1" precision="2" unit="[[unit_short_second]]">
        <input>off1</input>
      </value>
      <separator height="1"/>
      <value label="触发起始 2" size="1" precision="2" unit="[[unit_short_second]]">
        <input>on2</input>
      </value>
      <value label="触发结束 2" size="1" precision="2" unit="[[unit_short_second]]">
        <input>off2</input>
      </value>
      <separator height="1"/>
      <value label="触发起始 3" size="1" precision="2" unit="[[unit_short_second]]">
        <input>on3</input>
      </value>
      <value label="触发结束 3" size="1" precision="2" unit="[[unit_short_second]]">
        <input>off3</input>
      </value>
      <separator height="1"/>
      <value label="触发起始 4" size="1" precision="2" unit="[[unit_short_second]]">
        <input>on4</input>
      </value>
      <value label="触发结束 4" size="1" precision="2" unit="[[unit_short_second]]">
        <input>off4</input>
      </value>
      <separator height="1"/>
      <value label="触发起始 5" size="1" precision="2" unit="[[unit_short_second]]">
        <input>on5</input>
      </value>
      <value label="触发结束 5" size="1" precision="2" unit="[[unit_short_second]]">
        <input>off5</input>
      </value>
      <separator height="1"/>
      <button label="复位">
        <input type="value">1</input>
        <output>reset</output>
      </button>
    </view>
    <view label="多任务">
      <graph label="Trigger on events" labelX="任务数" labelY="事件间隔" unitY="[[unit_short_second]]">
        <input axis="x">tindex</input>
        <input style="vbars" lineWidth="0.9" axis="y">dtlist</input>
      </graph>
      <graph label="Trigger durations" labelX="任务数" labelY="持续时长" unitY="[[unit_short_second]]" scaleMinY="fixed" minY="0">
        <input axis="x">tindex</input>
        <input style="vbars" lineWidth="0.9" axis="y">ddlist</input>
      </graph>
      <value label="任务数" size="1" precision="0">
        <input>tindex</input>
      </value>
      <value label="平均间隔" size="2" precision="3" unit="[[unit_short_second]]">
        <input>avgInterval</input>
      </value>
      <value label="平均频率" size="2" precision="2" unit="[[unit_short_hertz]]">
        <input>avgRate</input>
      </value>
      <value label="平均频率（次/分钟）" size="2" precision="1" unit="1/min">
        <input>avgBPM</input>
      </value>
      <button label="复位">
        <input type="value">1</input>
        <output>reset</output>
      </button>
    </view>
  </views>
  <export>
    <set name="Raw">
      <data name="t (s)">t</data>
      <data name="Luma">amplitude</data>
    </set>
    <set name="Events">
      <data name="On (s)">onEvents</data>
      <data name="Off (s)">offEvents</data>
    </set>
  </export>
</phyphox>